Real Estate (Hospitality) Associate, Dubai, 5-8 PQE
Location:  --Dubai
This top ranking law firm is looking for a mid-senior associate in its Dubai offices.
This impressive Real Estate team offers a full range of services in areas including acquisitions and disposals, construction, financing, hospitality and leisure, land use, planning and development, but candidates most must have solid experience in hospitality and development.
Candidates should also have solid commercial experience and be self-starters.
UK qualified lawyers are preferred.
Should you wish to apply for this role, please contact Richard McLerie () for a confidential chat.
